== 早年生活 ==
赫德生長於[[德克萨斯州|德州]][[奧斯汀|奧斯汀]]。她的父親-{zh-cn:戴维;zh-hant:大衛;}-·克林顿·赫德（David Clinton Heard）任職於承包商，母親派翠莎·-{zh-cn:佩奇;zh-hant:佩基;}-（Patricia Paige）則是美國的網路研究員。她原就讀於聖米迦勒天主教高中，十一年級時輟學，全心投入好萊塢的演藝事業。赫德在青少年時期就十分活躍於學校的戲劇部門，常在當地的廣告和活動露面。16歲時，她的密友遭逢車禍身亡，同時受到[[艾茵·蘭德|艾茵·蘭德]]作品及當時男朋友的影響，原本信奉[[天主教|天主教]]的赫德遂轉為[[無神論|無神論者]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=Amber Heard will be heard |url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-05-29-amber-heard_N.htm |publisher=USA Today |date=2007-05-30 |author=William Keck |access-date=2010-12-09 |archive-date=2012-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120706123640/http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2007-05-29-amber-heard_N.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=profit>{{cite magazine|url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/aquaman-box-office-profit-2018-1202584701/|title=James Wan's $1B+ 'Aquaman' Became DC's Lifeboat After 'Justice League' Debacle: No. 5 In 2018 Most Valuable Blockbuster Tournament|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|magazine=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-03-28 |access-date=2019-03-29 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107225844/https://deadline.com/2019/03/aquaman-box-office-profit-2018-1202584701/ |url-status=live}}</ref>

